title: #110: Ask An Asian With Joe Jitsukawa
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another bizarro episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome from the Just Kidding News channel on youtube, Joe Jitsukawa, to discuss Asian Political Correctness and the world of Conspiracies.
Thank you so much for all of your support.
